# Production Architecture — canonical (2026-06-15)

**Authority:** [docs/architecture/MASTER-PRODUCTION-ARCHITECTURE.md](../../docs/architecture/MASTER-PRODUCTION-ARCHITECTURE.md)

## Products

| Product | API | Frontends |
|---------|-----|-----------|
| **TSC Platform** | `api.theshakticollective.in` (NestJS, Railway) | Website + Community (Vercel) |
| **CoreKnot** | `api.coreknot.in` (Express + workers, Railway) | CoreKnot client (Vercel) |

## Shared infra

Neon PostgreSQL · Redis · Clerk · PostHog · Sentry · Cloudflare (DNS + R2)

## Rules for agents

1. **Website/Community → Platform API only.** No CoreKnot API from public frontends.
2. **CoreKnot Client → CoreKnot API only.** No new CRM/task writes via Platform API.
3. **No new Mongo dependencies.** CoreKnot Mongo is sunset — see [MONGO-SUNSET-REPORT.md](../../docs/architecture/MONGO-SUNSET-REPORT.md).
4. **Deploy target:** Railway (APIs) + Vercel (frontends). Not Render.
5. **Repos:** `tsc-platform`, `tsc-coreknot`, `tsc-shared`, `tsc-infra`, `tsc-docs`. Deprecate `tsc-api`, `tsc-community`, `tsc-web`.
6. **Env templates:** `.env.platform.example`, `.env.coreknot.example`, `.env.shared.example`.

## Phase R0 (complete)

Platform API health, Swagger, ClerkAuthGuard scaffold, CI, Railway config — done. See archived [backend-stabilization-sprint.mdc](./backend-stabilization-sprint.mdc).

